      <hedline>
        <hl1>THE MARKETS: COMMODITIES</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Gold and other precious metals slump as gold producers in nations with weak currencies sell to raise dollars; graphs (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>GOLD TUMBLES.  Gold and other precious metals, priced in dollars, slumped as gold producers in nations with weak currencies sold to raise dollars. In New York, gold for December delivery fell $5.80, to $280.10 an ounce.</p>
      </block>
